25|$|As the United States Army Chemical Corps focused {{its efforts}} on the weaponization of sarin nerve agent (GB) during the 1950s the M34 cluster bomb was the first <b>such</b> <b>weapon</b> mass-produced by the Army. The weapon was the United States' first major nerve agent weapon after World War II.|$|R
